{"tid":2124103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比例代表制奧妙是不足額當選　建制派35+靠口味增多和拉闊　不是初選","createTime":"2020-07-25T07:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T07:11:39.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"057a05b956d1e2b7da662f82b878074b717e280f","tid":2124103,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200723110526/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276750294538313728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200723110526%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1276750294538313728&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=61e500a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200723110526/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276750294538313728</a><br />\n<br />\n在比例代表制下，除了得票數目達到門檻，肯定當選的足額議員，還有不足額當選，就算得票數未達門檻，仍有可能當選。依比例分配民意代表，理論上每個議席平分票數，但實際上很難個個齊頭數。既然少票已能當選，那麼分拆候選名單，政黨議席甚甚至陣營議席就會增加。建制派(親中派)就是這樣做，不是初選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200626184550/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276584671841673217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200626184550%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1276584671841673217&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=f5982e7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200626184550/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276584671841673217</a><br />\n<br />\n在比例代表制下，一方面，只要死忠數目足夠達到一個很低的門檻就可以當選，另一方面，有其他人光譜位置很近才會𠝹票，光譜位置遠丁點已不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200627055515/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276754505011363840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200627055515%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1276754505011363840&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=a0d46323\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200627055515/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276754505011363840</a><br />\n<br />\n上屆立法會正選，地區直選部份，在競爭激烈下，民主+本土陣營議席是增加的，單純是DQ使總議席數變少。地區直選，多名單會多議席。"},{"pid":"87b474e140f06ab8a1e3fda9147f99a47423ef00","tid":2124103,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6373c2bb54adbe632aa4ddf7b7d9486c734286c0","tid":2124103,"uid":289900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"你講得啱呀<br />\n比例代表制下只要死㩜一少數支持者就當選到<br />\n有班老屎忽aka黃碧雲因為咁可以不斷連任"}]}